history.content:
Shadow an Engineer applications are officially out! The Shadow an Engineer program connects students with companies to attend a virtual externship over spring break. Sign up to be paired with a company and get the chance to learn about the day-to-day experiences of engineers in industry, connect with professionals, and more. Externships will be held virtually from March 22-26, 2021. 
Application link: http://tinyurl.com/sae21app
Company information: https://tinyurl.com/saespring21
Deadline: February 26th at 11:59 PM PT
Participating Companies:
DocSend
ENGEO
General Motors
National Instruments (NI)
Neptune Medical
Sift
Tanium
Turnitin
If you have any questions, feel free to contact Jazmine at jazzr12@berkeley.edu or Jennifer at jennifersiyuanzhou@berkeley.edu.
